{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T11:29:12.521Z","seriesId":109125,"title":"serial experiments lain","thumbnailUrl":null,"descriptionFirst":"自殺した生徒からメールが届く。面白半分・恐さ半分で学校中の話題になっていた。人づきあいが苦手な玲音はこの日初めて数少ない友人・ありす達から聞かされ、それを知った。帰宅後、玲音は自分の部屋にある、まれにしか開くことのないNAVIを立ち上げる。はたして、そこには自殺した生徒・千砂からのメールが来ていた。\n\n岩倉玲音:清水香里／父・岩倉康雄:大林隆之介／母・岩倉美穂:五十嵐麗／姉・岩倉美香:川澄綾子／瑞城ありす:浅田葉子／山本麗華:手塚ちはる／加藤樹莉:水野愛日／四方田千砂:武藤寿美\n\n企画・原案:Production 2nd／オリジナルキャラクターデザイン:安倍吉俊／監督:中村隆太郎／脚本:小中千昭／キャラクターデザイン:岸田隆宏／アニメーション制作:トライアングルスタッフ／制作協力:GENCO／製作:GENEON ENTERTAINMENT\n\n©NBCUniversal Entertainment Japan\n\n次話→so36422929","tags":["アニメ","第一話","SF","ファンタジー","鬱アニメ","清水香里","1998年夏アニメ","中村隆太郎","安倍吉俊","SERIAL_EXPERIMENTS_LAIN","LAIN"],"cours":null,"colKey":"さ","relatedSeries":[{"seriesId":96474,"title":"神霊狩／GHOST HOUND","thumbnailUrl":null}],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so36422928","episodeNo":1,"title":"serial experiments lain　layer:01　ＷＥＩＲＤ","viewCounter":22639,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36422928/36422928.85112347"},{"contentId":"so36422929","episodeNo":2,"title":"serial experiments lain　layer:02　ＧＩＲＬＳ","viewCounter":7273,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36422929/36422929.92198881"},{"contentId":"so36423011","episodeNo":3,"title":"serial experiments lain　layer:03　ＰＳＹＣＨＥ","viewCounter":5655,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423011/36423011.47002097"},{"contentId":"so36423012","episodeNo":4,"title":"serial experiments lain　layer:04　ＲＥＬＩＧＩＯＮ","viewCounter":5071,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423012/36423012.53183755"},{"contentId":"so36423013","episodeNo":5,"title":"serial experiments lain　layer:05　ＤＩＳＴＯＲＴＩＯＮ","viewCounter":4631,"startTime":"2021-12-10T10:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/36423013/36423013.37663641"},{"contentId":"so364230